《'''外星人的日常'''》（{{lang-en|''Alien Worlds''}}）是一部[[英國|英國]]的{{le|紀錄劇情片|Docufiction}}，由[[蘇菲·歐克妮多|蘇菲·歐克妮多]]擔任旁白。使用[[電腦成像|CGI]]技術描繪，並透過由四集組成的[[迷你影集|迷你影集]]將事實與科幻要素結合，並通過將地球上的生命定律應用於想像中的[[太陽系外行星|系外行星]]，模擬出[[外星生命|外星生命]]的生活<ref>{{Cite web|last=Mallenbaum|first=Carly|title=Netflix in December 2020: What's new and what's expiring|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/tv/2020/11/24/netflix-december-2020-everything-new-the-prom-selena/6400544002/|access-date=2020-11-27|website=USA TODAY|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209081140/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/tv/2020/11/24/netflix-december-2020-everything-new-the-prom-selena/6400544002/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="forbes Sheena Scott Alien Worlds">{{cite news |last1=Scott |first1=Sheena |title=Netflix’s ‘Alien Worlds’: Fantastical British Mini Series Blending Facts With Fiction |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/sheenascott/2020/12/05/netflixs-alien-worlds-fantastical-british-mini-series-blending-facts-with-fiction/ |access-date=2 January 2021 |work=Forbes |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212110442/https://www.forbes.com/sites/sheenascott/2020/12/05/netflixs-alien-worlds-fantastical-british-mini-series-blending-facts-with-fiction/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該劇於2020年12月2日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上線<ref>{{Cite web|title=Alien Worlds {{!}} Netflix Official Site|url=https://www.netflix.com/title/80221410|access-date=2020-11-27|website=www.netflix.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206003353/https://www.netflix.com/title/80221410|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

